Requirements and Design Details

'x' = implemented 

Grid Properties 
•	 Export to XLS 
•	 Show count / Pagination (e.g.Page x of x) - https://www.ag-grid.com/javascript-grid/row-pagination/ 
•	 Edit Cell Value (for hours only)
•	 Resize layout with Container - https://codesandbox.io/s/github/rexebin/AgGridAutoResizeToFitContainer 
•	 Drag to top grid to set row groups 
•	 Show overlay loading pulling data - https://www.ag-grid.com/javascript-data-grid/overlays/ 

Row Properties 
•	 Alternating Row color 

Column Properties 
•	 Resizable Columns 
•	 Pin Columns 
•	 Filter Columns 
•	 Sort Asc/Desc by Column 
•	 Auto Size to Fit (on load) 
•	 Double click auto column resize 
•	 Shift resize (takes space from adjacent) 
•	 Hide Columns 
•	 Header tool tips 
•	 Validation on cell data 
•	 Column Grouping - https://www.ag-grid.com/javascript-data-grid/column-groups/ 
       * All the hours collapse into a single column which shows total forecast hours. 
*  Change Cell Color on update - https://stackoverflow.com/questions/39648623/how-to-change-color-of-ag-grid-cells-for-dynamically-changing-data
       * When a cell value changes from it's original value then the Cell color turns Red.

Optional Properties 
•	 Lock Column position (from move) 
•	 Lock resizing 
•	 Row Spanning (merge like function) 
•	 Pin Rows 
•	 Drag Rows 
•	 Display Rows per page option (25,50,100) 
•	 Toggle Light/Dark theme  - Light/Dark mode toggle with React using Context API and styled components - DEV Community 
 
